        <p>Specifies the severity level of changed content  in the drift report. Valid values are <code>BLOCKER</code>, <code>CRITICAL</code>, <code>MAJOR</code>, <code>MINOR</code>, and <code>INFO</code>; or 0–4. Overrides the value of <code>--drift-severity</code> for changed content only. <b>Default: <code>INFO</code></b>.</p>
